<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Are You Prepared? Classes, Fair to Help Residents Stay Safe During Disasters</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert
		
		<span class="date">Jan. 26, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="http://news.ucf.edu/resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2031/en_US/swaw main.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
			<p>Florida Severe Weather Awareness Week runs through Saturday, Jan. 30. </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400417c223ec20125ae9931fd0030a8">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
